{"tid":439569,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［日本仔萬歲］美日機械人大戰10點35分開始","createTime":"2017-10-18T02:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T03:46:25.000Z","uid":60341,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b35bd0dfececfda691d13d9104551408771fee83","tid":439569,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/102023_83588c1e6440b027aa98cc07f1b7f287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F102023_83588c1e6440b027aa98cc07f1b7f287.jpg&h=ac9df365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitch 網址：twitch.tv/megabotsinc<br />\n<br />\n官方 Facebook 網址：<a href=\"http://facebook.com/megabotsinc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fmegabotsinc&d=Fp0gW9q2H3tmsIhTXVHjeeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=5b27a2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/megabotsinc</a>"},{"pid":"ce3c734a94d5f866177b3cf5e3ddd22eb04b2070","tid":439569,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"美國同日本都各自有機械人愛好者，集結製作代表他們的巨型武裝機械人。根據最新消息，美、日兩部具有先進武器、機械結構的 MegaBots 與水道橋重工，會正式開打。而有關比賽狀況，會在美國時間 10 月 17 日在 Twitch 平台播放（之後陸續在其他平台播放），到時就會知道邊個國家製造的機械人夠厲害，並非得個講字！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這場決鬥可以說醞釀了兩年之久，美、日雙方一直在物流以及場地方面傷腦筋，不過在美國時間 10 月 17 日（香港時間 2017年10月18日上午10時），雙方機械人對決的情況將會正式上映。美國 MegaBots 與日本水道橋各自派出機械人，作出生死決戰。戰鬥過程將於 Twitch.tv 平台上進行首播。<br />\n<br />\n美國 MegaBots 將派出 4.8 米高、12噸重，全部機械零件由美國本土製造的「Eagle Prime」機械人應戰，而日本水道橋重工方面，就會派出高 4 米，重 6.5 噸的「Kuratas」出戰。單看噸位的話，似乎有名顯差距，但最後勝負好難講。<br />\n<br />\n然而現在擁躉們有一個巨大的問號，是這場比賽到底是直播還是錄播？在今年 9 月，MegaBots 在他們的 Facebook 就發表了帖文:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內容大意是：「我們活著回來，我們從決鬥中回來了，影片將會盡快上載，播映日期將會很快公佈。」在這帖文下面就有很多人詢問是否這場對決，只有錄影播放而不會搞直播。但無論如何，10 月 17 日（香港時間 2017年10月18日上午10時）肯定是第一次看到兩部機械人決戰的比賽情況，沽且到當日打開 Twitch 收看吧。Megabots 宣佈在 Twitch 播放後會在 YouTube、Facebook、Instagram、Twitter 上映。"},{"pid":"9d813444c1ac8e150cccd42d1fe7feff7ea3de22","tid":439569,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bfc6912d7f8a0a4d93c086a6181fce26a338ef","tid":439569,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:51:02.000Z","msg":"屌美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ae483c5b834adf635b003d535334c237aee23e","tid":439569,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e7c2b1142f0c6860503c8d7e10f5855c204c9","tid":439569,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:56:43.000Z","msg":"打未"},{"pid":"d6c57a3ba77a4001e903235043255ba229d01eae","tid":439569,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"596a3fa0066f96ad99fbcc7857cd5981b2dcb687","tid":439569,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70885538072a962ffcc8783f939f99838cd1666c","tid":439569,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"輸左 日本..."},{"pid":"d5d6b09281d4de6f8fc31b7ed65c7ed162309156","tid":439569,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"咁就完 屌"},{"pid":"92970bd50b22befa2552319ce4d36033e10738f9","tid":439569,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打未</blockquote><br />\n打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一下電鋸KO左日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802ccf57c9c094174a1691c4c73f94e13ea9c652","tid":439569,"uid":136097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime